WEBVTT

00:01:05.083 --> 00:01:09.583
<i>Nearly two years have passed</i>
<i>since this death game began.</i>

00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:14.417
<i>I'm still fighting alone</i>
<i>on the front lines.</i>

00:01:17.417 --> 00:01:21.042
<i>Akihiko Kayaba is out there somewhere,</i>
<i>watching this world.</i>

00:01:21.417 --> 00:01:23.958
<i>What is he feeling right now?</i>

00:01:29.042 --> 00:01:30.250
Guess I'll head home now.

00:01:42.458 --> 00:01:45.042
"October 17, 2024"       "Floor 74: Dungeon"

00:01:56.375 --> 00:02:00.792
<i>The cowardly past that I'd acknowledged</i>

00:02:01.167 --> 00:02:06.667
<i>Still not understanding why,</i>

00:02:07.000 --> 00:02:17.542
<i>I stand behind myself, scared</i>
<i>Projecting reality onto today</i>

00:02:17.875 --> 00:02:22.875
<i>I've drawn so many skies</i>

00:02:23.208 --> 00:02:27.583
<i>This must be my fleeting heart</i>

00:02:27.917 --> 00:02:30.292
<i>Out of control</i>

00:02:30.625 --> 00:02:35.875
<i>In my dreams, this body soars so high</i>

00:02:36.208 --> 00:02:41.042
<i>And it can brush away any fears that cling to me</i>

00:02:41.417 --> 00:02:47.583
<i>Asleep inside me, these budding</i>
<i>feelings start to expand</i>

00:02:47.917 --> 00:02:51.542
<i>I realize this, weak as I am...</i>
<i>As long as I had you</i>

00:02:51.875 --> 00:02:56.833
<i>I could stay strong in this dark world</i>

00:02:57.167 --> 00:03:02.833
<i>My heart will dream a long dream forever</i>

00:03:03.750 --> 00:03:06.208
<i>I want to always be with you</i>

00:03:06.542 --> 00:03:11.917
<i>I'll give you everything I have...</i>

00:03:15.000 --> 00:03:19.000
"The Sword Dance of Black and White"

00:03:33.458 --> 00:03:34.792
Is that...

00:03:52.417 --> 00:03:54.167
"Floor 50: Algade"

00:03:54.167 --> 00:03:56.083
"Floor 50: Algade"
Seriously?

00:03:56.083 --> 00:03:59.708
"Skull Powder" "Ragout Rabbit Meat"
"Lizardman Skin" "Lizardman Scales"
But this is an S-class rare item!

00:03:59.708 --> 00:04:02.958
I've never laid eyes on the
real deal till now either!

00:04:03.500 --> 00:04:04.958
Hey, Kirito.

00:04:04.958 --> 00:04:07.417
Don't you already have all
the money you need?

00:04:07.417 --> 00:04:11.250
Buy it off you? Wouldn't you
rather eat it yourself?

00:04:11.250 --> 00:04:12.625
I'd love to eat it.

00:04:12.625 --> 00:04:15.583
I'll probably never get
my hands on one again.

00:04:15.583 --> 00:04:16.583
In that case...

00:04:16.583 --> 00:04:20.167
But who has their cooking
skill high enough

00:04:20.167 --> 00:04:22.542
to prepare an item like this?

00:04:22.542 --> 00:04:25.708
Right... If we tried,
we'd just burn it...

00:04:28.792 --> 00:04:29.792
Kirito...

00:04:35.792 --> 00:04:36.917
Chef – captured!

00:04:36.917 --> 00:04:38.542
Wh-What?

00:04:41.083 --> 00:04:45.833
Hey! How unusual to see you
in a dive like this, Asuna.

00:04:45.833 --> 00:04:48.625
It's almost time for
the next boss raid...

00:04:48.625 --> 00:04:51.083
...so I just came to see
if you were alive.

00:04:51.083 --> 00:04:55.167
I'm on your friend list.
You can tell from that, can't you?

00:04:55.167 --> 00:04:57.250
As long as you're alive,
that's good enough.

00:04:57.542 --> 00:05:00.583
Anyway, what's going on?
Something about a chef?

00:05:00.583 --> 00:05:02.375
Oh, yeah.

00:05:02.375 --> 00:05:05.167
What's your current cooking skill?

00:05:06.667 --> 00:05:08.458
I maxed it last week.

00:05:08.458 --> 00:05:09.667
What?

00:05:09.667 --> 00:05:11.208
Amazing, right?

00:05:11.208 --> 00:05:13.917
If you're that good,
I have a favor to ask you.

00:05:19.792 --> 00:05:22.542
Th-This is a Ragout Rabbit!

00:05:22.542 --> 00:05:23.917
I'll trade you.

00:05:23.917 --> 00:05:27.375
If you cook it for me,
I'll let you have a bite.

00:05:29.583 --> 00:05:31.750
You'll. Give. Me. Half!

00:05:33.792 --> 00:05:35.000
O-Okay...

00:05:35.875 --> 00:05:37.000
All right!

00:05:40.042 --> 00:05:41.125
Sorry...

00:05:41.125 --> 00:05:43.250
This means our deal's off.

00:05:43.250 --> 00:05:47.125
We're buddies, right? Right?
At least let me taste it too...

00:05:47.125 --> 00:05:50.625
I'll write you a report
in 800 words or less.

00:05:52.292 --> 00:05:54.917
Oh, come on!

00:05:56.000 --> 00:05:58.333
So... where should
I do the cooking?

00:05:58.333 --> 00:06:00.333
Well...

00:06:00.333 --> 00:06:03.875
You probably don't have any decent
cookware at your place anyway, right?

00:06:05.333 --> 00:06:06.625
Just this once,

00:06:06.625 --> 00:06:10.917
considering the ingredient,
I wouldn't mind using my place.

00:06:13.208 --> 00:06:16.458
That will be all for today.
Thank you for your hard work.

00:06:16.458 --> 00:06:21.250
Lady Asuna, you can't let someone of such
dubious background accompany you home.

00:06:23.375 --> 00:06:27.167
I don't know about this guy's background,
but his skills are for real.

00:06:27.167 --> 00:06:30.708
He's probably at least 10
levels above you, Kuradeel.

00:06:30.708 --> 00:06:33.500
You're saying that I'm
inferior to such a guy?

00:06:34.375 --> 00:06:35.625
I see...

00:06:35.625 --> 00:06:37.167
He's one of those beaters.

00:06:38.708 --> 00:06:40.375
Yes, that's right.

00:06:40.750 --> 00:06:44.375
Lady Asuna, all they care
about is themselves!

00:06:44.375 --> 00:06:47.333
Nothing good will come of being
around someone like him.

00:06:48.458 --> 00:06:49.833
What's going on?

00:06:49.833 --> 00:06:51.958
That's Lightning Flash Asuna!

00:06:51.958 --> 00:06:53.792
You're right! She's really cute!

00:06:54.583 --> 00:06:57.375
Just go home for today.

00:06:57.375 --> 00:06:59.458
That's an order from
your vice commander.

00:07:02.333 --> 00:07:04.542
Hey, are you sure about this?

00:07:04.542 --> 00:07:05.542
I'm sure!

00:07:11.208 --> 00:07:14.708
"Floor 61: Selmburg"

00:07:16.375 --> 00:07:20.667
It's huge, and there's hardly anyone
else around. It's really liberating.

00:07:20.667 --> 00:07:23.458
Then why don't you move here too?

00:07:23.917 --> 00:07:26.792
Because I'm seriously lacking in funds.

00:07:27.875 --> 00:07:29.417
Anyway,

00:07:29.625 --> 00:07:32.750
are you really sure about
that guy back there?

00:07:32.750 --> 00:07:35.250
I said that I didn't want one,

00:07:35.250 --> 00:07:38.375
but our new policy is to provide
bodyguards to the higher-ups.

00:07:39.917 --> 00:07:43.750
Before, our guild members were
personally invited by the commander.

00:07:43.750 --> 00:07:45.833
We were just a small guild.

00:07:45.833 --> 00:07:48.917
But we began getting
more and more people.

00:07:48.917 --> 00:07:51.542
When we became known
as the strongest guild,

00:07:51.542 --> 00:07:53.292
things started getting weird.

00:07:56.375 --> 00:07:59.667
Well, it's not a big deal,
so don't worry about it!

00:08:00.708 --> 00:08:03.292
We should hurry, or it'll get dark.

00:08:03.292 --> 00:08:05.083
R-Right...

00:08:08.583 --> 00:08:10.958
E-Excuse me...

00:08:14.042 --> 00:08:16.708
Hey... How much did all this cost?

00:08:18.417 --> 00:08:21.792
The room and furniture were
probably around four million Col...

00:08:22.292 --> 00:08:24.042
I'm gonna go change,
so have a seat.

00:08:24.667 --> 00:08:26.333
O-Okay...

00:08:31.167 --> 00:08:33.083
Four million Col.

00:08:33.083 --> 00:08:35.333
Four megaCol.

00:08:35.917 --> 00:08:39.500
I'm sure I've earned
that much too, but...

00:08:46.583 --> 00:08:48.833
How long do you plan to
stay dressed like that?

00:08:49.083 --> 00:08:51.083
O-Oh, right...

00:08:56.333 --> 00:08:59.375
So this is a legendary
S-class ingredient?

00:08:59.375 --> 00:09:01.625
So how do you want it cooked?

00:09:01.625 --> 00:09:04.083
Chef's choice, if you please.

00:09:04.083 --> 00:09:05.958
Let's see...

00:09:05.958 --> 00:09:08.042
Then let's make a stew.

00:09:08.375 --> 00:09:09.375
Ragout...

00:09:09.750 --> 00:09:12.917
"To stew," as they say, after all!

00:09:23.875 --> 00:09:27.958
Normally, there'd be a lot more steps.

00:09:29.125 --> 00:09:33.458
But cooking in SAO is
oversimplified. It's boring.

00:09:36.208 --> 00:09:38.625
That takes care of the stew!

00:09:39.500 --> 00:09:41.750
Okay, I'm gonna make
some side dishes.

00:10:08.417 --> 00:10:10.292
I've been here two years,

00:10:10.292 --> 00:10:12.833
and this is the first time
I've ever eaten S-class food!

00:10:13.458 --> 00:10:16.625
I'm so glad that I've
survived this long.

00:10:16.625 --> 00:10:18.208
Yeah...

00:10:19.500 --> 00:10:20.958
It's strange...

00:10:20.958 --> 00:10:26.542
It kind of feels like I was born
and raised here my entire life.

00:10:26.542 --> 00:10:27.875
That's the sense I'm getting.

00:10:28.750 --> 00:10:33.333
Lately, there are days I can't
even remember the other world.

00:10:34.167 --> 00:10:35.958
And it isn't just me.

00:10:35.958 --> 00:10:41.750
These days, fewer and fewer people seem
desperate to clear the game or escape.

00:10:41.750 --> 00:10:45.583
Right now, there aren't
even 500 players left

00:10:45.583 --> 00:10:47.333
fighting on the front
lines, are there?

00:10:48.083 --> 00:10:52.292
Everyone has grown
accustomed... to this world.

00:10:54.500 --> 00:10:56.708
But I want to go back.

00:10:58.083 --> 00:11:01.625
After all, there are lots of things that
I never got the chance to do there.

00:11:02.833 --> 00:11:04.042
Yeah.

00:11:04.042 --> 00:11:09.333
We've got to do our best, or we can
never face the merchants and others

00:11:09.333 --> 00:11:11.583
who've been supporting us.

00:11:16.000 --> 00:11:17.583
Stop it.

00:11:18.375 --> 00:11:19.583
What?

00:11:19.583 --> 00:11:23.792
Several people with that same look
on their face have proposed to me before.

00:11:27.125 --> 00:11:30.458
From the look of things, you aren't
close to any other girls, are you?

00:11:32.250 --> 00:11:34.875
It's fine. I'm a solo player.

00:11:40.917 --> 00:11:43.792
You don't want to join
a guild, Kirito?

00:11:45.375 --> 00:11:48.667
I know the beta players
don't fit in with groups.

00:11:48.667 --> 00:11:49.792
But...

00:11:50.417 --> 00:11:52.625
Ever since we hit floor 70,

00:11:52.625 --> 00:11:57.042
there seem to be more and more
irregularities in the monster algorithms.

00:12:00.542 --> 00:12:04.875
There are unforeseeable things
that a solo player can't handle.

00:12:04.875 --> 00:12:07.917
And it's not like you can
always warp out.

00:12:07.917 --> 00:12:10.500
I keep a solid safety margin.

00:12:11.583 --> 00:12:13.708
And besides, in most cases,
party members

00:12:13.708 --> 00:12:17.458
are more likely to hinder me,
rather than help.

00:12:17.458 --> 00:12:18.458
Oh?

00:12:21.000 --> 00:12:24.042
I get it. You're the exception.

00:12:24.042 --> 00:12:25.042
Am I?

00:12:26.458 --> 00:12:29.208
In that case, party up with me.
It's been forever.

00:12:30.333 --> 00:12:32.500
Also, black is my lucky color this week.

00:12:32.500 --> 00:12:33.792
What's up with that?

00:12:33.792 --> 00:12:37.083
That's easy for you to say, Asuna...
but what about your guild?

00:12:37.083 --> 00:12:39.667
We don't have any leveling quotas.

00:12:39.667 --> 00:12:41.292
Th-Then what about
your bodyguard?

00:12:41.292 --> 00:12:42.292
I'll ditch him.

00:12:59.792 --> 00:13:02.125
"Asuna invites you to join her party."

00:13:06.833 --> 00:13:08.917
The front lines are dangerous.

00:13:14.042 --> 00:13:15.583
F-Fine.

00:13:22.500 --> 00:13:25.958
I suppose I should
thank you for today.

00:13:25.958 --> 00:13:27.542
Thanks for the meal!

00:13:27.542 --> 00:13:28.875
Likewise.

00:13:28.875 --> 00:13:31.750
I'd like to say,
"Help me out again,"

00:13:31.750 --> 00:13:34.375
but I doubt I'll find
something like that again.

00:13:34.375 --> 00:13:37.417
Well! Even normal ingredients can
be finessed if you have the skills.

00:13:43.542 --> 00:13:45.792
The way the world is now...

00:13:45.792 --> 00:13:51.792
Is this really what Akihiko Kayaba
wanted to create?

00:13:57.250 --> 00:14:01.500
"October 18, 2024"       "Floor 74: Calmdet"

00:14:02.208 --> 00:14:03.750
She's not coming.

00:14:09.125 --> 00:14:10.208
Watch out!

00:14:12.833 --> 00:14:15.000
Ow...

00:14:17.125 --> 00:14:18.125
What...

00:14:19.958 --> 00:14:30.958
...is this?

00:14:30.958 --> 00:14:32.417
Ouch.

00:14:43.583 --> 00:14:46.042
U-Um... Hey! Good morning, Asuna.

00:14:52.917 --> 00:14:53.917
What?

00:14:57.375 --> 00:15:00.625
Lady Asuna, it won't do to
have you take such liberties.

00:15:01.333 --> 00:15:03.292
Let's return to guild headquarters.

00:15:03.292 --> 00:15:04.583
No!

00:15:04.583 --> 00:15:05.958
And what were you doing

00:15:05.958 --> 00:15:09.250
staking out my house so early
in the morning anyway?

00:15:09.250 --> 00:15:13.083
I thought this might happen,
so for the past month,

00:15:13.083 --> 00:15:16.750
I've been carrying out my mission
of observing you within Selmburg.

00:15:16.750 --> 00:15:19.958
Th-That's not an order from
the guild commander, is it?

00:15:19.958 --> 00:15:23.208
My mission is to guard you.

00:15:23.208 --> 00:15:25.667
Needless to say, that
includes at your home.

00:15:25.667 --> 00:15:27.667
No, it doesn't, idiot!

00:15:28.958 --> 00:15:31.917
Please don't be so unreasonable.

00:15:32.875 --> 00:15:35.125
Now then, let's return
to headquarters.

00:15:40.500 --> 00:15:41.792
Sorry.

00:15:41.792 --> 00:15:45.958
I've got your vice commander
reserved for today.

00:15:47.000 --> 00:15:49.917
I'll take responsibility
for Asuna's security.

00:15:49.917 --> 00:15:53.000
It's not like we're going
on a boss raid today.

00:15:53.000 --> 00:15:55.250
You can go to headquarters alone.

00:15:55.250 --> 00:15:56.917
Don't mess with me!

00:15:56.917 --> 00:16:01.250
A low-level player like you
couldn't possibly protect her!

00:16:01.250 --> 00:16:03.750
I am a member of the glorious
Knights of the Blood Oath...

00:16:04.083 --> 00:16:06.083
I know I can do a
better job than you.

00:16:08.542 --> 00:16:11.250
If you're going to shoot off
your mouth like that,

00:16:11.250 --> 00:16:14.125
you're prepared to prove it, right?

00:16:15.042 --> 00:16:17.500
"Will you accept duel request?"
"Opponent: Kuradeel"
"Type: 1 vs. 1"

00:16:20.167 --> 00:16:21.708
Are you sure?

00:16:21.708 --> 00:16:23.042
It's fine.

00:16:23.042 --> 00:16:25.417
I'll report this to the
commander myself.

00:16:26.958 --> 00:16:28.292
"Normal Mode"
"Time-Limit Mode"
"One-Strike Mode"

00:16:31.500 --> 00:16:33.625
Watch carefully, Lady Asuna.

00:16:33.625 --> 00:16:37.500
I'll prove there's nobody capable
of protecting you besides myself.

00:16:42.208 --> 00:16:45.667
Kirito, the solo player, and a member of the
Knights of the Blood Oath are about to duel!

00:16:45.667 --> 00:16:46.917
This'll be fun to watch.

00:17:32.333 --> 00:17:34.042
I-Impossible...

00:17:39.750 --> 00:17:41.333
W-Wow.

00:17:41.333 --> 00:17:42.500
He destroyed the weapon.

00:17:42.500 --> 00:17:43.625
Was that deliberate?

00:17:45.208 --> 00:17:48.750
If you want to try with another weapon,
I'll be happy to take you on.

00:17:48.750 --> 00:17:50.417
But you've had enough,
don't you think?

00:17:59.708 --> 00:18:01.500
L-Lady Asuna...

00:18:04.375 --> 00:18:06.250
He cheated somehow!

00:18:06.250 --> 00:18:09.875
Destroying my sword... there must have
been some kind of trick behind that!

00:18:09.875 --> 00:18:14.708
Otherwise, I never would've
lost to a dirty beater like him!

00:18:15.292 --> 00:18:16.542
Kuradeel,

00:18:16.542 --> 00:18:19.292
I'm ordering you as vice commander
of the Knights of the Blood Oath.

00:18:19.667 --> 00:18:22.792
As of today, you are relieved
of your post as bodyguard.

00:18:22.792 --> 00:18:26.792
Stand by at guild HQ until you
receive further orders. That is all.

00:18:26.792 --> 00:18:28.792
Wh-What?

00:18:28.792 --> 00:18:29.792
You...

00:18:43.333 --> 00:18:45.750
Teleport: Grandzam.

00:18:59.708 --> 00:19:03.083
Sorry... for dragging you
into an unpleasant situation.

00:19:03.083 --> 00:19:05.250
No, it's fine.

00:19:05.250 --> 00:19:07.667
What about you? Are you okay?

00:19:07.667 --> 00:19:09.458
Yes.

00:19:09.458 --> 00:19:11.708
I think the guild seems so stifling now

00:19:11.708 --> 00:19:14.500
because of my focus on
clearing the game above all...

00:19:14.500 --> 00:19:18.167
...and because of the way I've been
forcing the rules on the other members.

00:19:19.958 --> 00:19:23.458
But... you had no choice really.

00:19:23.458 --> 00:19:28.417
If you hadn't been that way, your guild
would never have gotten this far.

00:19:30.458 --> 00:19:34.375
I just mess around as a solo player,
so I have no right to judge.

00:19:34.833 --> 00:19:35.917
Still,

00:19:35.917 --> 00:19:41.167
even if you decide to take a day off
to party with a slacker like me,

00:19:41.667 --> 00:19:45.333
I don't think that anyone would
have the right to complain.

00:19:48.708 --> 00:19:51.292
Well, I guess I'll say thanks.

00:19:51.833 --> 00:19:55.792
So I'll accept your offer
and take it easy today.

00:19:55.792 --> 00:19:57.000
You can play as forward.

00:19:57.000 --> 00:19:58.750
W-Wait a second!

00:19:58.750 --> 00:20:00.792
Aren't we supposed to
take turns as forward?

00:20:00.792 --> 00:20:03.208
I'll do it tomorrow!

00:20:08.208 --> 00:20:11.708
"Floor 74: Dungeon"

00:20:31.458 --> 00:20:34.708
Fighting in the vanguard is easier
with a skilled person here...

00:20:34.708 --> 00:20:36.417
Kirito, we're gonna switch now!

00:20:37.167 --> 00:20:38.167
Right!

00:20:56.500 --> 00:20:58.125
Kirito, look.

00:21:05.917 --> 00:21:07.542
Isn't that...

00:21:08.083 --> 00:21:10.042
It probably is.

00:21:10.625 --> 00:21:12.375
It's the boss room.

00:21:12.750 --> 00:21:13.833
What do we do?

00:21:14.375 --> 00:21:16.292
Should we just take a look?

00:21:16.750 --> 00:21:21.208
Boss monsters never leave
the rooms they guard.

00:21:21.708 --> 00:21:23.833
If we just open the door,
we'll be okay.

00:21:23.833 --> 00:21:25.792
R-Right.

00:21:25.792 --> 00:21:28.833
Have a teleport crystal
ready, just in case.

00:21:28.833 --> 00:21:30.208
Yeah.

00:21:31.958 --> 00:21:33.833
Ready? Let's open it.

00:21:33.833 --> 00:21:34.833
Yeah.

00:22:30.042 --> 00:22:41.542
<i>The tolling of the faraway bells</i>
<i>sounded a little lonely to me</i>

00:22:41.875 --> 00:22:53.375
<i>So I tried harder, one more time,</i>
<i>this time soaring higher, all the way up</i>

00:22:53.750 --> 00:22:59.292
<i>Neither this reality that just keeps repeating itself</i>

00:22:59.625 --> 00:23:05.125
<i>Nor all my wishes, as numerous as the stars</i>

00:23:05.542 --> 00:23:10.542
<i>Now that I've found the tomorrow</i>
<i>I should strive for</i>

00:23:10.875 --> 00:23:15.833
<i>None of them can overcome these feelings of mine</i>

00:23:16.167 --> 00:23:22.667
<i>A world without end, opening up before my eyes</i>

00:23:23.000 --> 00:23:26.625
<i>Even if it's no more than a dream</i>

00:23:27.125 --> 00:23:33.833
<i>Even if I'm still lost, deep in my heart, it is strong</i>

00:23:34.208 --> 00:23:39.667
<i>Echoing forever and ever</i>

00:23:40.000 --> 00:23:46.208
<i>Shining softly, ever so softly</i>

00:23:47.000 --> 00:23:53.067
Next Time: "The Blue-Eyed Demon."
